oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Copy print photograph of a group of men posed by an American train in France
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Copy print photograph of a mixed group of people that includes American soldiers, French civilians and one woman standing by the tender of an American locomotive in France. The man in uniform, kneeling third from the right, may be Jessie Rice. From the photo collection of Jessie Owen Rice, an air service mechanic near Paris (France).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Rice, Jessie Owen
